---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Header from '../components/layout/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro'
---
<Layout title="Terms of Service — LRA CloudOps" description="Terms of Service for LRA CloudOps." lang="en">
  <Header lang="en" />
  <section style="background:#F8F9FA;padding:3rem 1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid #DADCE0;">
    <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
      <p style="font-family:'Red Hat Text',sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;color:#1A73E8;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Legal</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p style="font-family:'Red Hat Text',sans-serif;font-size:1rem;color:#5F6368;">Last updated: July 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section style="background:#FFFFFF;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;font-family:'Red Hat Text',sans-serif;font-size:1rem;color:#5F6368;line-height:1.8;">
      <h2 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">1. Services</h2>
      <p>LRA CloudOps provides DevOps consulting and infrastructure security audits. The free audit is provided as-is without warranty of completeness.</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">2. Consulting services</h2>
      <p>Monthly consulting (€699/month) may be cancelled with 7 days notice. Project-based work is invoiced upon delivery.</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">3. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>LRA CloudOps maximum liability is limited to the amount paid for the specific service.</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">4. Governing law</h2>
      <p>These terms are governed by the laws of Spain. Disputes shall be resolved in Las Palmas de Gran Canaria, Spain.</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Red Hat Display',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#202124;margin:2rem 0 1rem;">5. Contact</h2>
      <p><a href="mailto:info@lracloudops.com" style="color:#1A73E8;">info@lracloudops.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>
